NOTE ON DATA:
This license covers the source code and the authors' own outputs (data-split
index files and result CSVs) in this repository. It does NOT cover the ToMBench,
ToMi, OpenToM, SocialIQa, or Hi-ToM benchmark datasets, which remain under their
respective original licenses and are NOT redistributed here. The result CSVs have
had the raw benchmark question text removed for this reason; obtain the original
data from the sources cited in the paper to reconstruct full inputs.
